{"tid":1387364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最需要既唔係錢同裝  而係 你都著埋防具  一齊場內場外分擔恐懼","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:16:10.000Z","uid":105976,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f6c7875d1acfb6c1ee39eb19af070eb2e01bcc","tid":1387364,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:47:57.000Z","msg":"香港人大把錢  到時裝備一定供過於求<br />\n和理非  冷氣軍師  上一代  要養家  有負擔 <br />\n唔係出左錢俾班後生就得    <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地需要每一個人<br />\n<br />\n無論你落唔落場   都帶/戴住防具<br />\n你唔落場唔驚被逗更加要做  <br />\n當條街唔少人將防具日常化 <br />\n黑警就好難去搜捕捉人<br />\n<br />\n我知一開始好難理破心理關口  <br />\n就戴d唔顯眼既先   護腿 護肘  之後掛個頭盔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92dd10e597c9dfc9e4395dd9abdcdce46cc3f394","tid":1387364,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb92e0c825a29478c89d8ae736e373f6b141a10","tid":1387364,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7969bcc55d2097df1482e0ba5c5e782d85411641","tid":1387364,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj